DemoAPP folder include libs and demo app. 


ijkplayer github: https://github.com/bbcallen/ijkplayer
openssl 1.0.1g github: https://github.com/devpack/openssl-android

Build ijkplayer with openssl:
1.主要步驟為:
git clone https://github.com/bbcallen/ijkplayer.git ijkplayer-android-stable
cd ijkplayer-android-stable
git checkout -B stable n0.1.1

./init-android.sh

cd android
./compile-ffmpeg.sh
./compile-ijk.sh

cd ijkmediaplayer/jni
ndk-build

# import android/ijkmediaplayer for MediaPlayer-like interface (recommended)
# import android/ijkmediawidget for VideoView-like interface (based on Vitamio UI)
# import android/ijkmediademo for VideoActivity demo (Simple VideoActivity)
2.修改compile-ffmpeg.sh加入openssl的路徑(可参考附件)


直接使用ijkplayer:
1.將DemoApp路徑下的project直接import
2.ijkmediaplayer和ijkmediawidget為library
3.ijkmediademo為執行程式
